2023 PLEASE slow down..We officially have a college senior and we are NOT okay!!👩🏽‍🎓🥹

Yesterday’s Senior Day at @radfordu was one for the books. Our baby “Kennedy” cheered her last official basketball game at Radford and I couldn’t be more happier for her. She’s been cheering since the tender age of “4” and she’s now on her way to graduating in May in hopes & prayers of sharing her gifts and talents with other cheerleaders/athletes in the future. 

S/o to her cousins, friends and family for always being there to support her cheer shenanigans for ALLLLL of these years LOL! Kennedy I’m beyond proud of you & can’t wait to watch you bloom into the AMAZING young woman that you are🤩 Congratulations on all of your hard work I love you Stink😍 

Mom❤️😘

MOD•ish/ is officially a “P-Element” Concept Salon.✨

Providing my clients with top tier products that can cater to ALL of their needs is my #1 priority, Especially being that my clientele is 50% natural & 50% relaxed hair💁🏽‍♀️

Being a suite owner it’s very important to me that I only use product/color lines that are significant to my clients hair needs & square footage because of limited space/storage!!! (Shampoo Holders can be found in my Amazon Store..LINK IN BIO)

I’d LOVE to hear some feedback from some of you that has ever used any of @patric_pelementproducts Aren’t they the 💣.com??!!!💥🔥 #pelement #patricbradley #healthyhair #modish

And which one are you???😆 I gotta admit for someone who stands all day to make a living, Cudos to all of you that has to sit In front of a computer all day. I’d probably be doing the most around my laptop as well🤣😭

This is why having a nice comfortable & relaxing salon experience is one of my top priorities for my clients. Love you ladies 4 LIFE!! Happy Thursdayyy IG Fam!!🫶🏽❤️✨ #salonlife #itsalifestyle #modish

Slowing it down a bit to show my appreciation for my @patric_pelementproducts So Soft Relaxer system & P-Levels Lightening System🤩 That allowed me to create this beautiful color story for my client just in time for her trip to Jamaica💁🏽‍♀️💞

Still on a high from last weekends celebration for my parents “40th Wedding Anniversary”🤩 

One thing me & my sister knew was that it was going to take everything in us to try to surprise them because we’re all just so close. But there’s no better way I would’ve wanted to celebrate my “10yr Salon Anniversary” than to dedicate it to our AMAZING parents but tricking them into a surprise celebration 🙌🏽❤️
